content.detailedDescription:
Just arrived home from work got out of my car and was looking at the nice clear sky and off in the distance to the west i glanced at 3 stars in a group and just as i was looking away i thought to my self was that one moving? i looked back and to my surprise it was, in fact moving south at a very high rate of speed compared to a jet.
i immediately grabbed my phone to note the time, it was 2:43am and thought to myself i need to get it on camera and tried but my samsung galaxy s3 couldn't pick it up so all i could do is watch and observe. 

it was small dimmer star like, just like the stars it was around and others in the sky. it traveled south several miles much faster than a jet, then slowed and about 45/60 seconds later a very large bright white flash either came from it or to the east side of it (between it and me), i thought i saw a trail of light coming up to the flash, only the last few hundred feet to the flash, but wasn't sure if it was just my eyes from the flash or not because it was so bright, it then turned west (away from me) and rapidly faded away on a slightly upward angle.

light possibly a missile fired at it? who knows, but it sure reminded me of a video i seen looking from space and seeing a ufo traveling around earth at about the same speed as my siting and seeing what looked like a missile being shot at it from earth and it changed direction and bolted at a extremely high rate of speed. 
very very similar to my siting except missile not as definite.
content.summary: Small dimmer star like, traveled south and slowed, bright white flash from it or to the east side of it, turned west and rapidly faded away.

april 19 20016 i was working in the shop separate from the house of a distance of 100 foot. i had begun working about 3pm that day until almost midnight when for unknown reasons i was drawn to the side door.( cell phone was recording from a previous video i made of the shop. the phone was set down on a cluttered work table along with my firearm.) i felt as if i was in a fog. i then woke up on my back on the drive way to my house absent my cell phone and firearm 3 hrs later with my keys separated into both hands and the neck of my jacket pulled down to my elbows limiting my movement.  seeing the stars and the outside garage light i knew where i was and unalarmed yet could not understand how i got there and why i was on my back side. i used my keys to get in the house and noticed light coming from my elderly mothers room and surprised she was awake but groggy with my pittbull in bed with her. i immediately asked her what time it was and she replied 3:20 am and she asked where my phone was (i didn't know) and then asked where my side arm was (again i didn't know)  
 at this point i think i freaked out a little and threw my keys from a loss of words and then began to tell her its here it got me its evil and it did something to me ive lost three hours and that my aunt who had just passed away was right. after regaining some composer we both went into the garage where she covered me with her side arm from the garage door so that i could retrieve mine. barn lights were off, door was unlocked, fire arm and cell phone recovered yet battery was depleted. once back inside we took pictures of my back my head and my arm because it hurt to the bone when touching the skin. i had multiple red dots almost the size of a penny on my upper scalp and strange markings on my back. mother had the shape of orions belt and another dot on the back of her right arm.
 the next day i charged my phone and noticed i had 2 hours and 29 minute blacked out video including human and non human language as well as sounds of me fighting with something verbally with responses. you can also clearly here my dog deeply barking from inside mothers room yet she does not remember any of it and cant believe she slept through the helicopters that had been circling as well as some ungodly loud deep pulsating hum descend and then ascend twice. we have a boot prints  high on the door of the shop and very strange huge boot prints in the gravel as well as very small feminine prints in front of the shop. 
i my self am a military trained combat vet as well as the rest of the males i descend from. i have three hours of missing time and a 2.5 hour recording of some of what happened to me.
 someone needs to contact me from your organization with the cell phone number provided i will submit the audio/video and the photos to help me get more answers as something was clearly done without my consent. if it had not been for the recording i would have not known other people and other nonhuman entities were performing a procedure on me. my identity needs to remain anonymous as this was a joint operation not just a close encounter. thank you. jc

content.detailedDescription:
In may 2014 i was at work as a health care assistant in stanhope, i had just got a patient up out of bed and taken him outside for a cigarette. the weather was warm with a near clear sky apart from a few small whispy clouds. i commented to the patient on how nice it was and looking up to the sky i noticed two copper coloured spheres with no appendages at all and no form of propulsion, at first i thought they were grouse or ducks but there was no sign of wings, the sun was glinting off the top left hand quarter of both spheres, which made me think they were balloons or chinese lanterns but they were moving against the wind and cloud direction they also kept a constant distance apart from each other during the fifteen seconds duration. the spheres maintained a constant slow straight speed neither ascending or descending nor making any noise at all.
 i told the patient what i was seeing as he could not see due to a building in the way and being wheelchair bound ,i also mentioned that i thought they were strange and nothing like i had seen before.
 both the spheres entered a small transparent whispy cloud where they either disappeared or faded away as they did not exit the cloud which should of only took three to five seconds to do this due to the small size of the cloud. i mentioned this to my patient straight away,i stopped outside another three to five minutes but the spheres did not reappear.
content.summary: Two spheres moved east to west against the wind,disappearing into a cloud.

content.detailedDescription:
It was a very strange event...Static electricity seemed to be everywhere, but there was no source.  the craft was solid, real and produced no noise, but it was just like the photo...A top shaped craft, hovering behind a tree...This is not my fist encounter with something strange.  the ship was watching, and was close enough to get a clear photograph.  it was near the top a b.C. evergreen, about a 200 foot tree, and causing all kinds of weird electrical/static effects in the area.

i saw the ufo and got a photo, then it left.  when looking at photo, there were all sizes of orbs in the area, and some that had geometrical patterns inside...

also, one had definite shapes inside, images that when zoomed in looked like building.

the circle is across from the ufo, and is in the branches of the tree...About in the middle of the picture, an inch or so from the edge.  it needs to be zoomed in on to see the images, which look like buildings with windows and doors where they would normally be.

the orbs were almost more startling that the ufo itself, as they are very strange, different sizes, and some have elaborate geometrical shapes.  also, it was a hot night, with no clouds...The moon is visible, but around the area of the trees near the ship, you cannot see any stars.  i played with the contrast settings and got some odd effects, things that showed the horizon, but also showed these orbs below the tree line in the distance.  i include the original photo, so play with zoom and contrast to see the strange objects, and photos that show the ufo clearly.  i snapped the photo with the flash on, but the craft didn't move...It seemed like it was watching me.  i also had weird dreams, all about the energy sources i think about all the time involving harnessing atomic engines/turbines on the nano scale.  i saw a perfect engine that would do everything i pictured, but i'm not an engineer, and have no way build one.
content.summary: Hovered above me...Hiding behind tree branch until i snapped photo.

content.detailedDescription: I was driving home from work heading west on highway 72. as i approached cr 735 to make a right turn i noticed a hyper white object in the sky. i pulled my car over and got out to observe it. the sky was almost perfectly clear with a few light sparse clouds. the object stood out. i stood perfectly still and observed a cylindrical object with rounded corners (tic tac shape) spinning slowly. it widen as the sides faced me and dimmed as the edges faced me. i moved so that the object was sitting directly above a power pole. this let me see that it was perfectly still while spinning on its horizontal axis. it remained locked on its position for over 3 minutes then slowly descended while moving north. it remained spinning without ever slowing or speeding up. it continued to descend until it dipped below the tree line and i lost sight of it. i took 3 photos but none show the object as it was hard to see the screen to aim the shot while the sun was shining on it. the object seemed to spin at about 50-60 rpm which is why the pictures may not have captured it as it was turning and not very visible as the edges faced me.
content.summary: White cigar craft spins hovering

content.detailedDescription: I was in my garden at 5 05pm just before sunset, looked up at 1/2 moon high in the east, when i noticed a very bright flash, it dimmed then disappeared momentarily, before brightening up again. first i thought it was a plane high up in the sky, but it was stationary!! it continued reflecting the sun on and off for 12 minutes until it disappeared. it's path was gradually to the north east but very slow moving. i think it may have been ascending. it seemed to be metallic, triangular in shape, and kept like rotating and reflecting the sun. was intrigued and ran and grabbed my binoculars for a better look, it was then i noticed like a sting dangling down with something attached to the end of it. my conclusion is that it was some type of balloon, weather balloon most likely, but was extremely high in altitude. eventually it just faded away. i had a witness and am retired airline pilot.
content.summary: Looked up at 1/2 moon and saw to the left a bright light dimming like a reflection from the setting sun,

content.detailedDescription:
I had downloaded a song by deadmau5. i was fully engrossed in it, i felt elated jumping on my open rooftop. then something shining caught my eyes. i saw an object hovering in the air quite above the line of sight. i didn't know what to do as i was mesmerized. it changed its colour between red and orange. it was quite afar but i could make out the shape. and believe me, we do not have weather balloon here nor drone. i punched the camera icon on my smartphone which takes a little seconds to launch and that shining thing was gone.
i remember that it was pitch dark, no moon, no stars. it was around 09:22-09-25 pm (ist) and i believe it is too late for evening star to show up. i quickly texted my friends on my whatsapp group. they made fun of me but luckily one fellow corroborated and next day my female friend told me that her brother saw something glowing up in the sky. he said he didn't want to believe what he saw. i didn't want to come out before cause i thought i would be laughed at. i believe in what i saw, whatever it was, it was really beautiful. luckily for me i took the screenshot of my whatsapp chat and the other guy responded.

content.detailedDescription: I was smoking and looked up to see a strange orange light.  i didn't think much of it at first but when i looked back up it had become almost seahorse shaped.  i started watching it closely at this point as it turned boomerang shaped.   as it changed shape it decreased in size and luminosity.  here and there i could see orbs flying away from it at various trajectories and speeds.  it then turned into 3 dim starlite objects and eventually into something that you would think was a star or a satellite.  it started getting brighter again and reformed into the boomerang/starfish shape again.   it repeated what happened before only faster this time until it was a dim star again and then completely disappeared.  was this a fleet?  i've seen weird stuff in the sky before but nothing this odd or unsettling.
content.summary: Orange object.  smaller break off.

content.detailedDescription:
I was sitting on my back patio deck at about 10:45 - 10:50 when i witnessed someting against the black backdrop of the sky. 

i was sitting in a fold out chair and from my deck, my view from ne to se is obscured by my neighbor's tree. i have a small (10-20 degree) view of the northern sky before the back of my home bocks my view to the northwest sky.
 
i just happened to be staring into the sky when something caugth my eye to the north. the object was boomerang shaped, had no lights and was only noticable because it was reflecting some city light. it was barely a few shades lighter than the night sky behind it, but no doubt it was there.

it appeared to be in a bank, as if in a turn from w to nw because i could make out a very distinctive boomerang shape. like looking at a plane from the side when is in a turn, it's wings are banked so you see more shape profile than if it were in level flight.

there were no lights and there was no sound. i estimate the object to be within 2 miles to the north of my location near 150th and penn in edmond, ok. i cannot be positive about this as i could not make out the object's size relative to my surroundings. it was too dark and barely visible.

in all, i witnessed th eobject for about 15-20 secs before it was obscured by the city lights on the horizon as it seemed to settle into a nw heading. 

i have never witness anything like this and i cannot rationalize it. i though it could be a military craft, but there was no sound whatsoever. i have lived next to an air force base and military craft make plenty of sound, even in the distance. for a moment, i though some idiot was hang gliding in the middle of the night, but found it unlikely per federal aircraft regulations, part 103.

my point is that i will be trying to figure out what i saw for a while. i hope there is a simple explaination, because what i fear it was scares me.
content.summary: Boomerang shaped object in the sky over edmond, ok at night.
